    "Each convolutional layer's output is fed into an activation function, which creates nonlinearity.",
    "Depthwise convolution layerIn case of a multi-channel image,a convolution layer works as follows: A single convolution operation getsF (i, j) = (I * K)(i, j) = � m � n I(i + m, j + n)K (m, n)performed on all the channels.",
    "Consider an image of dimension 3*256*256 and filter 3*3*3, the entire cube filter gets applied on the image cuboid.",
